title: My Love Affair With David Lynch And Peachy Like Nietzsche: Dark Clown Porn Snuff for Terrorists And Gorefiends
description: This is the novella My Love Affair with David Lynch by Jason Rogers and Peachy Like Dark Clown Porn Snuff for Terrorists and Gorefiends , the short story collection by David Tamarin.This is absurd, surreal, dark, demented, and bizzaro literature at its...well...most screwed up.
author: Jason Rogers
